Highway To Heaven Hill Climb Time Trial
That Dam TT aka The Prettyboy Reservoir Time Trial
description: A time trial race around the Prettyboy Reservoir watershed in northern Baltimore county.
course: Start on Spooks Hill Road 0.2m west of Rayville Road, continue on Prettyboy Dam Road, Right on Traceys Store Road, right on Foreston, continue on George's Creek Road, continue on Gunpowder Road, right on Beckleysville Road, right on Spooks Hill Road to Rayville Road.
notes: Our 50K/31M course travels along the roads through and around the Prettyboy Reservoir. The course has approximately 1,600 ft of climbing and therefore it is not a guarantee that a TT bike will have the fastest time for any category. Equipment choice will be paramount when planning your race which is exactly why we do not have a "Merckx" category for our race.
directions: Parking/Stage: Rayville road between Middletown & Spooks Hill Roads, 0.3 miles north of Spooks Hill Road.
